commits.sourceNew:
/** * Initializes the iterator. This method must be called before any calls to * {@link #skipTo(int)}, and its return value indicates whether there are * any relevant documents for this iterator. If it returns false, any call * to {@link #skipTo(int)} will return false as well.
* NOTE: calling this method twice may result in skipping over * documents for some implementations. Also, calling it again after all * documents were consumed may yield unexpected behavior. */ public boolean init() throws IOException;
